sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant API as FastAPI Gateway
    participant S3 as Object Store (S3)
    participant Q as Job Queue (Celery/Redis)
    participant W as Worker (Vision + Agents)
    participant DB as Postgres

    U->>API: GET /uploads:presign
    API-->>U: presigned URL
    U->>S3: PUT photo (direct, bytes never touch API)
    U->>API: POST /projects/{id}/analyze (s3_key, prefs)
    API->>DB: create job row (status=queued)
    API->>Q: enqueue job_id
    API-->>U: { job_id }
    U->>API: WS subscribe /jobs/{job_id}/stream

    Q->>W: run pipeline(job_id)
    W->>DB: status=running, node=vision
    W->>W: scene → segmentation → metric depth → plant ID
    W->>W: spatial reasoning → SiteModel
    W-->>API: event: measurements_ready
    API-->>U: stream measurements
    W->>W: suitability scorer → ranked plants (+breakdown)
    W-->>API: event: recommendations_ready
    API-->>U: stream recommendations
    W->>W: depth+mask render (one variant)
    W->>S3: store render
    W->>W: BoM + cost
    W->>DB: persist SiteModel, variant, cost; status=done
    W-->>API: event: done
    API-->>U: stream final report
